310
00:11:45.780 --> 00:11:48.180
El avance de los alemanes hacia la frontera

311
00:11:48.180 --> 00:11:49.460
francesa

312
00:11:49.295 --> 00:11:50.894
tampoco le produjo alarma.

313
00:11:51.295 --> 00:11:52.735
En vano su cuñada,

314
00:11:52.815 --> 00:11:54.415
